r2002 | abbyz | 2008-12-16 08:36:53 -0800 (Tue, 16 Dec 2008) | 4 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/3rd_party/Makefile.in

kexec compilation fails with a few undefined references to xen functions. kexec finds xen devel libraries and tries to build xen support, 
but the LIBS flag in Perceus overrides the libraries required to build kexec (-lxenctrl in this case). 


