------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1920 | gmk | 2008-08-23 23:02:09 -0700 (Sat, 23 Aug 2008) | 2 lines
Changed paths:
   M /perceus/1.4/modules/ipaddr/50-ipaddr.pl

Support where no options are given.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1919 | gmk | 2008-08-23 22:46:44 -0700 (Sat, 23 Aug 2008) | 11 lines
Changed paths:
   M /perceus/1.4/modules/ipaddr/50-ipaddr.pl
   M /perceus/1.4/modules/ipaddr/activate

Enhance the ipaddr Perceus module so that it can support configuration
options per device. For example, now we can do things like:

   n0000 eth0(MTU=9000):[default]/[default]

Or bridge devices on NSA:

   n0000 vmbr0(TYPE=bridge&ENSLAVE=eth0):[default]/[default]

It also now supports autoprobing the default gateway.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1918 | gmk | 2008-08-16 23:26:03 -0700 (Sat, 16 Aug 2008) | 2 lines
Changed paths:
   M /perceus/1.4/scripts/lib/Perceus/Vnfs.pm

