------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1546 | gmk | 2008-01-30 22:10:06 -0800 (Wed, 30 Jan 2008) | 5 lines
Changed paths:
   M /perceus/1.4/3rd_party/patches/dnsmasq-2.38-ipoib-clid.patch

Found another case where the PXE client was adding a ClientID to the
DHCPDISCOVER thus causing a different address to be provided by dnsmasq
then what /etc/hosts stated. Dnsmasq was being too smart and didn't
want to create a conflict. This is a minor lobodomy.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
